nodes.text: Trypto Buball was a male alien agricultural baron who made his fortune on his family's vast farming colonies of space-fungi. Buball was present in the Canto Bight casino in 34 ABY.

Trypto Buball first appeared in Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi, with Star Wars: The Last Jedi: The Visual Dictionary, written by Pablo Hidalgo, identifying the character. He was portrayed by Aidan Cook with animatronic performance by Patrick Comerford.[source?]
